## Exceptions

### packages/pdf-server (AGPL-3.0)

The `@swibostyle/pdf-server` package is licensed under AGPL-3.0 due to its
dependency on Vivliostyle. See [packages/pdf-server/LICENSE](./packages/pdf-server/LICENSE)
for details.

### tests/fixtures (Mixed)

Sample content in `tests/fixtures/` is from SWIBO Fictions and has separate
licensing terms (CC-BY 4.0 for content, MIT for code).
See [tests/fixtures/LICENSE](./tests/fixtures/LICENSE) for details.
